1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 12]

2
00:00:16,075 --> 00:00:18,395
[Zhou's residence]

3
00:00:18,420 --> 00:00:19,659
Whose fault is this?

4
00:00:19,660 --> 00:00:20,579
He's never been involved in business!

5
00:00:20,580 --> 00:00:21,459
As everyone knows,

6
00:00:21,620 --> 00:00:23,139
all affairs of the Zhou family

7
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:25,579
are managed by my incompetent brother,

8
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:27,259
Zhou Yichen.

9
00:00:27,580 --> 00:00:28,459
In recent years,

10
00:00:28,900 --> 00:00:30,259
my father has been unwell

11
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:32,019
and had no involvement in this matter.

12
00:00:32,540 --> 00:00:33,139
Therefore,

13
00:00:33,540 --> 00:00:34,739
this substitution of inferior goods

14
00:00:34,820 --> 00:00:35,819
is solely my brother's doing!

15
00:00:35,820 --> 00:00:37,299
A total disgrace to our family!

16
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:38,379
He deserves punishment.

17
00:00:39,380 --> 00:00:40,579
As both the pride of Wu County

18
00:00:41,060 --> 00:00:42,619
and the king of teas,

19
00:00:42,820 --> 00:00:44,099
Baihao Yinzhen should

20
00:00:44,140 --> 00:00:45,379
be beyond targeting, right?

21
00:00:45,620 --> 00:00:46,739
What's your point here?

22
00:00:46,740 --> 00:00:47,979
Give us a solution.

23
00:00:48,060 --> 00:00:49,059
Everyone,

24
00:00:50,580 --> 00:00:51,819
one bad apple

25
00:00:51,940 --> 00:00:53,059
doesn't spoil the whole barrel.

26
00:00:54,260 --> 00:00:55,499
Our shared vision

27
00:00:55,700 --> 00:00:57,299
is to expand Wu County's tea business!

28
00:00:57,300 --> 00:00:58,179
and make it stronger,

29
00:00:58,580 --> 00:00:59,699
taking it beyond China

30
00:00:59,700 --> 00:01:00,939
to the world stage.

31
00:01:01,100 --> 00:01:01,779
That makes sense.

32
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:03,899
That's reasonable.

33
00:01:03,900 --> 00:01:04,899
Agreed.

34
00:01:05,740 --> 00:01:07,059
So regarding this matter,

35
00:01:07,500 --> 00:01:08,899
I will work with my father

36
00:01:09,020 --> 00:01:09,939
to handle it fairly,

37
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:11,619
and give you all an answer.

38
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:13,339
We'll recover the 10,000 catties

39
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:14,499
of Baihao Yinzhen

40
00:01:14,500 --> 00:01:15,539
my brother hoarded privately,

41
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:17,259
restoring our overseas reputation.

42
00:01:17,580 --> 00:01:18,259
Additionally,

43
00:01:18,820 --> 00:01:19,699
anyone who places

44
00:01:19,820 --> 00:01:21,139
an order today

45
00:01:21,820 --> 00:01:22,619
will receive

46
00:01:22,620 --> 00:01:24,579
an unprecedented partnership discount.

47
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:27,699
You'll be able to purchase

48
00:01:28,140 --> 00:01:28,699
the king of teas,

49
00:01:28,700 --> 00:01:30,619
Baihao Yinzhen, at second-grade tea prices.

50
00:01:42,780 --> 00:01:43,339
Dad,

51
00:01:45,220 --> 00:01:46,339
you're not upset with me, are you?

52
00:01:46,980 --> 00:01:48,899
It was your brother's mess to begin with.

53
00:01:49,100 --> 00:01:50,419
You've never been involved.

54
00:01:51,180 --> 00:01:52,379
It was the right call

55
00:01:53,540 --> 00:01:55,379
to have you step in on this matter.

56
00:01:57,740 --> 00:01:59,859
He passed off 10,000 catties of

57
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:00,979
ordinary tea as premium grade,

58
00:02:00,980 --> 00:02:02,019
which cost him his good name.

59
00:02:02,380 --> 00:02:03,219
What was he after?

60
00:02:03,340 --> 00:02:04,339
I don't know.

61
00:02:04,740 --> 00:02:05,539
Moreover,

62
00:02:05,780 --> 00:02:06,859
where did he get

63
00:02:06,860 --> 00:02:08,099
so much ordinary tea?

64
00:02:08,420 --> 00:02:09,459
Wu County is large,

65
00:02:09,780 --> 00:02:11,779
but I haven't found any purchase records.

66
00:02:11,980 --> 00:02:13,099
How strange.

67
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:14,219
In my opinion,

68
00:02:15,220 --> 00:02:16,259
we should stop investigating.

69
00:02:16,940 --> 00:02:17,779
Stop?

70
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:22,259
Why?

71
00:02:22,700 --> 00:02:23,739
Family matters

72
00:02:24,020 --> 00:02:25,299
are still largely unknown to you.

73
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:26,859
There's much you don't know,

74
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:28,059
so stop asking.

75
00:02:29,060 --> 00:02:30,259
When the time comes,

76
00:02:30,860 --> 00:02:32,259
you'll understand.

77
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:36,739
Since you say so,

78
00:02:36,740 --> 00:02:37,899
I won't ask any more questions.

79
00:02:39,940 --> 00:02:40,539
Master.

80
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:42,739
Third concubine and Fifth concubine have arrived.

81
00:02:42,820 --> 00:02:43,699
I don't want to see Wanzhi.

82
00:02:44,260 --> 00:02:45,179
Call Fifth concubine in.

83
00:02:45,500 --> 00:02:46,099
Yes.

84
00:02:48,980 --> 00:02:49,699
Master.

85
00:02:49,820 --> 00:02:50,539
I...

86
00:02:59,380 --> 00:02:59,979
Master.

87
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:01,179
I'll apologize on behalf of Chen... 
- Out!

88
00:03:02,300 --> 00:03:03,939
Master, please don't be angry with him.

89
00:03:03,940 --> 00:03:04,539
Out!

90
00:03:04,940 --> 00:03:05,539
Third concubine.

91
00:03:05,940 --> 00:03:07,819
You know Master's temper.

92
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:10,379
Better not anger him further.

93
00:03:10,780 --> 00:03:11,379
Please.

94
00:03:20,580 --> 00:03:21,299
Master.

95
00:03:21,580 --> 00:03:23,059
I heard you were ill.

96
00:03:23,140 --> 00:03:24,139
I came specifically to see you.

97
00:03:24,460 --> 00:03:25,459
It's nothing serious.

98
00:03:28,300 --> 00:03:29,659
You call this nothing serious?

99
00:03:30,020 --> 00:03:31,259
You're coughing up blood.

100
00:03:32,860 --> 00:03:33,619
Eldest Young Master.

101
00:03:35,260 --> 00:03:36,779
I should take care of Master.

102
00:03:40,620 --> 00:03:42,779
I finally have a chance to serve my father.

103
00:03:43,220 --> 00:03:44,499
Let me take this duty, concubine.

104
00:03:57,620 --> 00:03:58,779
This accident needs

105
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:01,139
to be dealt with quietly.

106
00:04:02,300 --> 00:04:03,019
Understood.

107
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:21,859
Steward.

108
00:04:23,060 --> 00:04:23,699
What did

109
00:04:25,020 --> 00:04:25,979
my father say?

110
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:28,419
Young Master, please sit.

111
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:32,779
Young Master.

112
00:04:33,340 --> 00:04:34,739
You did well today.

113
00:04:35,020 --> 00:04:36,339
Taking all the blame.

114
00:04:36,980 --> 00:04:38,659
Preserving Master's reputation.

115
00:04:39,140 --> 00:04:39,819
Remember

116
00:04:40,420 --> 00:04:41,979
You are the Zhou family's great benefactor.

117
00:04:42,740 --> 00:04:44,019
Master won't forget it.

118
00:04:45,540 --> 00:04:46,339
However...

119
00:04:47,140 --> 00:04:49,459
you need to resolve the stain

120
00:04:50,100 --> 00:04:52,739
of substituting inferior goods yourself.

121
00:04:53,460 --> 00:04:54,779
Please tell Father for me.

122
00:04:56,220 --> 00:04:57,739
I won't disappoint him.

123
00:04:58,540 --> 00:04:59,659
Remember, Young Master.

124
00:05:00,700 --> 00:05:03,219
This is Master's final chance for you.

125
00:05:05,980 --> 00:05:06,579
Steward.

126
00:05:08,580 --> 00:05:09,219
How is

127
00:05:10,340 --> 00:05:11,779
Father's health?

128
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:13,779
I'm very worried about him.

129
00:05:13,980 --> 00:05:14,579
Young Master.

130
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:17,979
I think you should worry more about yourself.

131
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:21,299
And more about those ten thousand dan of goods.

132
00:05:37,980 --> 00:05:39,219
I understand.

133
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:43,099
Tea is the Zhou family's lifeblood.

134
00:05:43,420 --> 00:05:44,499
Even if it's a family scandal,

135
00:05:44,740 --> 00:05:46,699
Master Zhou should spare no effort

136
00:05:46,780 --> 00:05:49,179
to track down those ten thousand dan of Baihao Yinzhen.

137
00:05:51,820 --> 00:05:53,019
There's only one possibility.

138
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:55,059
He's

139
00:05:55,780 --> 00:05:56,899
aware of it too...

140
00:05:59,660 --> 00:06:01,379
We can't rule out a bigger scheme.

141
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:05,499
It's too late.

142
00:06:05,660 --> 00:06:06,619
I must return to Zhou Manor.

143
00:06:06,860 --> 00:06:07,619
Let me walk you out.

144
00:06:09,980 --> 00:06:10,739
Don't move.

145
00:06:28,740 --> 00:06:29,179
Fifth concubine

146
00:06:31,420 --> 00:06:32,299
Zhou Yichen.

147
00:06:34,420 --> 00:06:35,739
Why are you colluding with this actress

148
00:06:35,740 --> 00:06:36,659
to target me?

149
00:06:37,300 --> 00:06:38,259
I don't understand.

150
00:06:38,900 --> 00:06:39,979
Do you even realize what you've done?

151
00:06:40,300 --> 00:06:41,379
Do you have any idea

152
00:06:42,780 --> 00:06:44,139
how many people you've hurt?

153
00:06:44,740 --> 00:06:46,419
I won't deny my hands are dirty.

154
00:06:47,020 --> 00:06:48,019
But to you,

155
00:06:49,900 --> 00:06:51,379
I have a clear conscience.

156
00:06:52,780 --> 00:06:54,019
What exactly do you want?

157
00:06:54,660 --> 00:06:55,659
I want you to testify

158
00:06:55,660 --> 00:06:57,499
that Zhou Yimo and An He colluded in secret

159
00:06:57,780 --> 00:06:59,139
to seize the headship of the family.

160
00:06:59,380 --> 00:07:01,259
They forged account books to frame me.

161
00:07:04,500 --> 00:07:05,259
Testify?

162
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:07,859
How can I testify against them?

163
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:12,019
Doesn't An He have a child?

164
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:14,779
If Marshal Lu finds out

165
00:07:15,140 --> 00:07:16,259
that the woman he loves

166
00:07:16,260 --> 00:07:18,259
had a child with another man,

167
00:07:18,980 --> 00:07:20,899
and that the father is Zhou Yimo,

168
00:07:21,500 --> 00:07:22,739
how would he feel?

169
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:27,179
Fifth concubine

170
00:07:27,780 --> 00:07:29,019
We're both in the Zhou family.

171
00:07:29,180 --> 00:07:30,299
Our fates are intertwined.

172
00:07:30,660 --> 00:07:31,899
If you help me this once,

173
00:07:32,420 --> 00:07:32,859
in the future, we...

174
00:07:32,860 --> 00:07:33,779
Zhou Yichen!

175
00:07:33,980 --> 00:07:35,979
Someone like you deserves to go to hell!

176
00:07:35,980 --> 00:07:38,259
Even at death's door, you're still defiant.

177
00:07:40,420 --> 00:07:41,379
Try this.

178
00:07:41,700 --> 00:07:43,939
Opium is a wonderful thing.

179
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:45,739
If you're willing to help me,

180
00:07:46,900 --> 00:07:48,179
everything will be fine.

181
00:07:49,300 --> 00:07:49,979
Open your mouth.

182
00:07:51,180 --> 00:07:52,059
Open your mouth.

183
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:54,819
Fifth concubine!

184
00:07:54,820 --> 00:07:56,459
I agree.

185
00:08:01,420 --> 00:08:02,779
I'll give false testimony for you.

186
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:06,459
But I made the fake account books.

187
00:08:08,380 --> 00:08:09,259
Put all the blame

188
00:08:09,260 --> 00:08:10,379
on me.

189
00:08:11,340 --> 00:08:12,459
Her child is still young.

190
00:08:13,220 --> 00:08:14,059
Spare her.

191
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:16,299
Blame you?

192
00:08:17,620 --> 00:08:19,419
You'd sacrifice so much for her?

193
00:08:20,860 --> 00:08:21,699
Is it worth it?

194
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:23,619
I beg you.

195
00:08:39,380 --> 00:08:40,139
Brother.

196
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:42,019
When did you become so impulsive?

197
00:08:43,060 --> 00:08:44,739
You risk your life to save her,

198
00:08:44,980 --> 00:08:46,219
isn't that impulsive?

199
00:09:09,340 --> 00:09:10,099
You go first.

200
00:09:10,140 --> 00:09:10,779
Brother.

201
00:09:11,020 --> 00:09:12,259
You hired assassins.

202
00:09:12,460 --> 00:09:13,499
The evidence is solid.

203
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:15,259
Prepare to meet your end.

204
00:09:21,700 --> 00:09:23,339
Since I can't keep her here,

205
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:25,739
you won't take her away either.

206
00:09:53,180 --> 00:09:53,859
Police!

207
00:09:53,980 --> 00:09:54,699
Stop!

208
00:10:03,540 --> 00:10:04,339
Captain Yu.

209
00:10:05,820 --> 00:10:06,659
He's injured.

210
00:10:08,460 --> 00:10:09,299
Help me.

211
00:10:12,220 --> 00:10:12,859
You two.

212
00:10:13,060 --> 00:10:13,819
Take him to the hospital.

213
00:10:32,780 --> 00:10:33,819
Ye Zhiqiu.

214
00:10:37,860 --> 00:10:38,939
I want to tell you...

215
00:10:38,940 --> 00:10:39,659
Shut up.

216
00:10:40,900 --> 00:10:41,779
Tell me after

217
00:10:41,780 --> 00:10:42,779
you've recovered.

218
00:10:45,300 --> 00:10:46,779
I'm afraid if I don't say it now,

219
00:10:47,860 --> 00:10:49,019
it'll be too late.

220
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:51,139
Zhou Yimo.

221
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:53,779
Zhou Yimo, listen to me.

222
00:10:54,780 --> 00:10:55,939
If you can't hold on,

223
00:10:56,540 --> 00:10:57,339
I swear

224
00:10:57,340 --> 00:10:59,099
I'll never listen to you again.

225
00:11:00,420 --> 00:11:01,579
We're almost at the hospital.

226
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:03,179
Hold on.

227
00:11:03,820 --> 00:11:04,699
You must hold on.

228
00:11:18,260 --> 00:11:19,459
The bullet's position is difficult to access.

229
00:11:19,540 --> 00:11:20,579
It's too close to the heart.

230
00:11:20,900 --> 00:11:22,099
The situation looks grave.

231
00:11:22,420 --> 00:11:23,619
Please prepare yourself mentally.

232
00:11:50,380 --> 00:11:51,499
Would you like me to take

233
00:11:52,020 --> 00:11:53,099
these damn shackles off for you?

234
00:11:56,500 --> 00:11:57,859
Whatever you want to do,

235
00:11:58,020 --> 00:11:59,019
I can help you.

236
00:11:59,460 --> 00:12:00,699
I can protect you.

237
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:08,699
There's already someone in my heart.

238
00:12:09,380 --> 00:12:10,859
I swear on my life

239
00:12:11,380 --> 00:12:12,259
that every word

240
00:12:12,780 --> 00:12:14,339
is true.

241
00:12:29,380 --> 00:12:30,459
The bullet is out.

242
00:12:30,620 --> 00:12:31,619
The patient is out of danger.

243
00:12:31,740 --> 00:12:32,659
Continue the blood transfusion.

244
00:12:33,180 --> 00:12:34,099
Understood.

245
00:13:23,020 --> 00:13:23,979
When did you get here?

246
00:13:25,180 --> 00:13:26,379
How can you care for him so much?

247
00:13:27,420 --> 00:13:29,059
He might be the one who killed your sister.

248
00:13:29,060 --> 00:13:29,699
He's not.

249
00:13:31,860 --> 00:13:33,139
What if I were lying there?

250
00:13:33,940 --> 00:13:34,819
Would you cry for me?

251
00:13:35,220 --> 00:13:36,139
Like you did just now?

252
00:13:37,020 --> 00:13:37,939
Yu Shi'an, what are you doing?

253
00:13:38,780 --> 00:13:39,339
Let go of me!

254
00:13:40,020 --> 00:13:40,739
Answer me.

255
00:13:41,580 --> 00:13:42,539
Why won't you answer me?

256
00:13:44,220 --> 00:13:45,539
Because he's the young master of the Zhou family?

257
00:13:47,420 --> 00:13:49,019
Or because you refuse to forgive me?

258
00:13:50,180 --> 00:13:50,979
Your issues

259
00:13:52,220 --> 00:13:53,139
at the police station,

260
00:13:54,940 --> 00:13:56,899
as the family, have nothing

261
00:13:57,220 --> 00:13:58,139
to do with me.

262
00:13:58,900 --> 00:14:01,099
I only want everyone who hurt my sister

263
00:14:01,340 --> 00:14:02,099
to pay the price.

264
00:14:02,580 --> 00:14:03,259
You've helped me,

265
00:14:03,540 --> 00:14:04,499
and I'm grateful.

266
00:14:05,020 --> 00:14:05,739
But in the future,

267
00:14:06,300 --> 00:14:07,499
please don't interfere anymore.

268
00:14:10,780 --> 00:14:11,779
After all that,

269
00:14:12,460 --> 00:14:13,659
you still won't answer my question.

270
00:14:14,900 --> 00:14:15,579
That's guilt, isn't it?

271
00:14:16,860 --> 00:14:17,699
You love him, don't you?

272
00:14:22,980 --> 00:14:23,539
Yu Shi'an,

273
00:14:24,780 --> 00:14:26,179
is there nothing in your world

274
00:14:27,780 --> 00:14:28,819
but love?

275
00:14:28,980 --> 00:14:29,339
Yes.

276
00:14:30,660 --> 00:14:31,859
And I only feel this way for you.

277
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:33,419
Since childhood,

278
00:14:33,420 --> 00:14:34,379
it's always been this way.

279
00:14:36,060 --> 00:14:36,859
I've always believed

280
00:14:37,260 --> 00:14:38,099
that only with you

281
00:14:38,700 --> 00:14:39,939
can my life be complete.

282
00:14:41,900 --> 00:14:42,659
So please!

283
00:14:43,220 --> 00:14:44,139
don't fall for anyone else.

284
00:14:45,540 --> 00:14:46,139
Whatever he can give you,

285
00:14:46,140 --> 00:14:47,099
I can give you too.

286
00:14:47,100 --> 00:14:47,699
Okay?

287
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:50,339
Captain Yu,

288
00:14:51,100 --> 00:14:52,459
please observe proper decorum

289
00:14:52,620 --> 00:14:53,619
with the Fifth Concubine.

290
00:15:04,460 --> 00:15:05,299
Captain.

291
00:15:19,340 --> 00:15:20,459
please don't tell anyone

292
00:15:20,900 --> 00:15:22,219
about what happened earlier.

293
00:15:22,780 --> 00:15:23,419
Understood.

294
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:24,859
Rest assured, Fifth Concubine.

295
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:25,619
I will

296
00:15:26,020 --> 00:15:27,339
keep it secret.

297
00:15:32,700 --> 00:15:33,459
Your mother has been

298
00:15:33,460 --> 00:15:34,499
worried sick,

299
00:15:34,500 --> 00:15:36,139
looking all over for you.

300
00:15:36,380 --> 00:15:37,779
That gave Zhou Yimo the opportunity

301
00:15:37,780 --> 00:15:38,819
to seize the chance.

302
00:15:40,260 --> 00:15:41,179
Chen,

303
00:15:41,260 --> 00:15:41,979
this time

304
00:15:41,980 --> 00:15:43,419
it's really troublesome.

305
00:15:45,700 --> 00:15:46,819
Lieutenant Zheng, you...

306
00:15:46,820 --> 00:15:47,619
Sit down.

307
00:15:51,700 --> 00:15:52,819
The Marshal decided

308
00:15:53,140 --> 00:15:55,019
to personally try prisoner Zhou Yichen.

309
00:15:55,460 --> 00:15:56,579
I heard he's with you,

310
00:15:56,780 --> 00:15:58,339
so I'm here to take him into custody.

311
00:15:58,580 --> 00:15:59,779
Isn't he right here?

312
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:00,699
Take him away.

313
00:16:01,100 --> 00:16:02,219
Hold on!

314
00:16:03,620 --> 00:16:04,299
Lieutenant Zheng,

315
00:16:04,420 --> 00:16:05,019
Zhou Yichen is

316
00:16:05,020 --> 00:16:06,779
the second young master of the Zhou family.

317
00:16:07,140 --> 00:16:08,979
I don't think that's appropriate.

318
00:16:09,260 --> 00:16:10,619
Over the years, Zhou family

319
00:16:10,620 --> 00:16:11,739
has sent the Marshal many gifts.

320
00:16:11,740 --> 00:16:12,859
Anyone who dares to stop us

321
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:14,219
will be shot dead.

322
00:16:15,940 --> 00:16:16,499
Uncle!

323
00:16:16,700 --> 00:16:17,339
Wait!

324
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:20,379
Lieutenant Zheng,

325
00:16:20,500 --> 00:16:22,059
you have some nerve.

326
00:16:22,700 --> 00:16:24,859
How dare you try to snatch him on my turf!

327
00:16:25,260 --> 00:16:26,019
Chief Zhou,

328
00:16:27,420 --> 00:16:28,259
I just found a secret

329
00:16:28,940 --> 00:16:31,019
warehouse belonging to Zhou Yichen.

330
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:35,059
And seized a batch of opium.

331
00:16:37,460 --> 00:16:39,019
This is Zhou's missing

332
00:16:39,020 --> 00:16:40,819
ten thousand dan of green tea.

333
00:16:41,540 --> 00:16:43,659
And there's a large quantity of opium.

334
00:16:44,020 --> 00:16:46,299
On the surface, they run a tea business,

335
00:16:46,820 --> 00:16:47,819
but in reality,

336
00:16:47,820 --> 00:16:49,619
they're also dealing in opium.

337
00:16:53,580 --> 00:16:54,379
Zhou Yimo

338
00:16:54,380 --> 00:16:55,939
is most likely

339
00:16:56,420 --> 00:16:57,579
the one who had

340
00:16:58,020 --> 00:16:58,859
the five thugs killed

341
00:17:00,420 --> 00:17:01,539
at his family's docks.

342
00:17:02,820 --> 00:17:03,939
Do you have any evidence?

343
00:17:04,180 --> 00:17:06,179
A custom-made knife you carry personally

344
00:17:06,620 --> 00:17:07,859
perfectly matches the fatal wounds

345
00:17:07,860 --> 00:17:09,059
on the head's

346
00:17:09,060 --> 00:17:10,379
of those five dead thugs.

347
00:17:11,180 --> 00:17:11,939
Yu Shi'an,

348
00:17:12,180 --> 00:17:13,179
have you lost your mind?

349
00:17:14,020 --> 00:17:15,459
Passing off inferior goods

350
00:17:15,820 --> 00:17:16,819
is still a minor matter.

351
00:17:18,180 --> 00:17:19,539
Kidnapping and murder

352
00:17:21,500 --> 00:17:22,259
are crimes

353
00:17:22,980 --> 00:17:25,899
that carry the death penalty.

354
00:17:26,060 --> 00:17:27,179
These cases

355
00:17:28,020 --> 00:17:28,939
must be handled together.

356
00:17:29,100 --> 00:17:29,579
Move!

357
00:17:30,260 --> 00:17:31,019
Uncle!

358
00:17:31,540 --> 00:17:32,219
Uncle!

359
00:17:32,860 --> 00:17:33,619
Uncle!

360
00:17:33,940 --> 00:17:34,819
Yu Shi'an,

361
00:17:35,620 --> 00:17:37,019
is this your first day working for me?

362
00:17:38,220 --> 00:17:39,979
Daring to push my nephew into the fire?

363
00:17:39,980 --> 00:17:41,099
Do you want your job?

364
00:17:42,180 --> 00:17:43,979
If you don't want it, you're fired!

365
00:17:46,300 --> 00:17:48,179
Ouch!

366
00:17:52,140 --> 00:17:53,299
Are you stupid?

367
00:17:54,380 --> 00:17:55,419
I quit!

368
00:18:01,460 --> 00:18:02,019
Here you are.

369
00:18:10,820 --> 00:18:11,499
Marshal,

370
00:18:12,420 --> 00:18:14,619
I will walk through fire and water for you

371
00:18:14,620 --> 00:18:15,499
without hesitation.
